=> brew tap udacity/CarND-MPC-Project https://github.com/udacity/CarND-MPC-Project
=> brew tap brewsci/science https://github.com/brewsci/homebrew-science

Go to /usr/local/Homebrew/Library/Taps/brewsci/homebrew-science/Formula , copy scotch.rb and scotch5.rb.
Paste the above two files into /usr/local/Homebrew/Library/Taps/udacity/homebrew-carnd-mpc-project folder
Then:
=> brew untap brewsci/science
=> brew install ipopt --with-openblas

